headline.main: Malaysia Wants Change in Venue for North Korea Qualifier
headline.print_headline: Malaysia Wants Change in Venue for North Korea Qualifier

lead_paragraph: Malaysia have asked that an Asian Cup qualifier against North Korea be moved to a neutral venue, as relations between the two countries worsen after North Korean leader Kim Jong Un's estranged half-brother was killed in Malaysia.
